  "prompt": "Do you think Quora app is slow and crashes sometimes?",
  "response": "User experiences with the Quora app can vary widely. Some users report that the app can be slow or prone to crashing, which may be due to various factors such as device compatibility, app version, or overall device performance. If you are experiencing issues with the Quora app, it's a good idea to check for updates, clear the app cache, or reinstall it to potentially resolve any performance problems. Additionally, user feedback on platforms like app stores can provide insights into common issues and whether they are being addressed by the developers.",
